<br>
Personally I think trials are far better than the mindless key camping in previous expasions. I prefere killing stuff to gain entrance to zones over 100+ hours of farming greens any day.<br>
<br>
Yes, it's difficult to pass without a guild backing you up, but it's doable. I've seen quite a few unguilded people and members of lower level guilds in PoS/PoV. Worst come to worst, get to 65 in a tier1 plane, then try the trials again. <br>
