The only problem I really have is that AA's, 60, 61, 62 are very reasonable exp grinds in PoD or PoN for example. You can get your spells there as well.<br>
<br>
63-65 and the related spells almost require higher level tiers if you don't have 8+ hours a day to spend on levelling. Who would want to grind out 63, 64 and 65 in the right courtyard of PoD or on Hobgoblins in PoN?<br>
